author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what's been happening with one of the biggest gaming movements in terms of preservation. Stop Killing Games took everyone by storm last year and since then a lot of games have survived, some are still dying and the future remains uncertain. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: What Happened To "Stop Killing Games"...
